            <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
                
                <p n="1">
                    Fortune!
                </p>
                
                <p n="1-3">
                    Fourteenth year of Tantippōttaraiyar.<note>Sanskrit Dantin + Tamil Pōttaraiyar. That is, the Pallava king Dantin.</note>
                </p>
                
                <p n="4-7">
                    <supplied reason="subaudible">This is</supplied> the sluice that Nakkaṉ, son of Kōṭṭaṅ<gap reason="lost"/>ntar, who lives residing in Āṟṟūr, in the Neṭuṅkalnāṭu, <supplied reason="subaudible">itself</supplied> in the Ītūrkkōṭṭam, had made.
                </p>
                
                <p n="8-9">
                    Kuvaṇataccaṉ <gap reason="lost"/> Ceyantaṉ.
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
